Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,TS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:04.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we going to start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:06.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It took me a while to think it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think we should start with Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:14.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the girl who does vocals for the guerrilla live concerts in the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you remember her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:23.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s always so energetic, laughing away while she bullies Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:26.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She does the band’s vocals and anything else she likes doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:30.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she’s already found peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:34.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just give her a gentle push,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,she’ll be able to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:38.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, then alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let’s do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's it going on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it took some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Sonic, version 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hand Sonic version 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:01.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks more evil than angelic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:07.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it like this because you told me I’m playing the cruel Angel, so I had to make it look mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:07.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:10.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s great. Really unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:11.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unpleasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:13.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, I mean really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:17.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you also grow wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’d look cool, wouldn’t it?{check かっちょいい}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to look cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:27.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just thought it would make you more Angel{\fnNyala}-{\fn}like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:31.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do this —
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:40.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You appear while she’s in band practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:41.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,then you tell her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Another club is complaining about the noise.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:47.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you point at Yui and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Your guitar is especially bad.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Because of you, the band is dead.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,“That being the case, I’m confiscating that guitar.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:02:00.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you take her guitar and leave the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Yui will give chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:05.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run, and head to the inner garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:11.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At that point I’ll pretend to bump into you, and then you let go of the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take it, so just run away at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way we can create a situation where I can be alone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just wait for the start of rehearsal and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Study block A {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Empty Classroom}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:43.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, don’t just keep going when you mess up the rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:49.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you should concentrate on just singing or playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:52.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah you’re right, it sounds bad right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasawa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san sang and played at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because Iwasawa was good at both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m trying my best too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:05.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re all too strict!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our concerts are popular aren’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a new song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your guitar, the band is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She discovered the band’s weak point in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t underestimate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows music! {She understands sound? hmm :/}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:32.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I thought nobody noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, I’m confiscating that guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn’t chase me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Without the guitar you don’t go off beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't it sound kind of weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We need a rhythm guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we get another side guitar player then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:20.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The band has the most impact with the vocals also on guitar, dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She made Hisako{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san angry! {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get my guitar back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:25.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dammit, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, that’s too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine, not a scra—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai protected it from Angel for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go, dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what’s with the “dammit!”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you’re doing whatever you want, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever I want? Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got the vocal position in the band, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re even playing guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:19.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that’s nothing, it’s just one of the things I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Lots”...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No wait, let’s talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Main Dining Hall {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Front}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t want to talk about it, that’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s okay, I’ll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:50.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have more things I want to do than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn’t do them when you were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:04.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was small, I got hit by a car from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:08.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I became paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t live without assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was constantly relying on my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always thinking it wasn’t fair to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:32.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to watch TV, so when I saw bands on music shows I thought it’d be great if I could do that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That turned out well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what else do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I watched baseball matches a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we already play baseball at the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t get a hit though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:50.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:51.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t be happy till you hit a home run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:02.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I become better in the band, I’m thinking about putting in some real practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping both of those up will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I’ll ask, what else was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was popular, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it was, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:15.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has too many interests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:19.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In what world does a person try to be a musician, baseball player, and a soccer player?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t suppose there are any oth—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pro wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In what world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, everything she wants to do comes from TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is going to be hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Granting all of those dreams for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:38.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll fulfill those dreams for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s start with something easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go with pro wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:48.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pro wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,German Suplex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way you can pull off such a flashy move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:56.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a pin or something you can actually pull off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:08:00.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ve always wanted to do the German Suplex!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll win with a sleeper hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t say such violent things so innocently!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:09.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re stronger than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:23.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it’s impossible for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you almost did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can we try it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:43.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go somewhere with grass first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I’ll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn’t joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I’ll get it right next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:07.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even able to pull off a bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was the root of the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this I nearly lost consciousness several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll start with bridge training then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s terrible, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ve never done this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can’t do this, you won’t be able to do the German Suplex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Several hours later}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m doing it, just about!{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're shaking all over the place, but that’ll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her arms are fixed firmly around my waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no escape from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:06.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,German Suplex!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Match over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it... I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:28.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:31.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How much more of this am I going to have to deal with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Study Block {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Passageway}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we do soccer next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A one on one penalty kick should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to do a dribble shoot against 5 people! {check 五人抜きのドリブルシュートじゃなきゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Maradona. {norg: fucking fuck I don’t understand sports terminology lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey TK, know where Matsushita 5th Dan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:13.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He can’t dance in my world right now.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me cry!{................................... die you SOB}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:16.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Secluded mountain training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Secluded mountain training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s gone pretty far off... {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So he won’t be back for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah whatever, you’ll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you gather up 4 other members for me?{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Study Block C {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Men’s toilet}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:41.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this secret from Yuri, but I got this letter from Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t even stand up to a single girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is absurd to think you call yourself a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m surprised you know a word like “absurd”.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you cured of idiocy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even idiots can read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:59.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll beat your girly ass till you learn some guts for the sake of sportsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be waiting after school at the soccer grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really write this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:12.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel now isn’t like the one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:17.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After having all those minds mixed into her, she's taken to writing challenges as idiotic as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t deal with this stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to go tell Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said keep it a secret from Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell Yuri, it’ll develop into another bloodbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:32.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it says “for the sake of sportsmanship” right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s saying she wants to fight fair and square with sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:39.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why this challenge is directed at us guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling Yuri would damage our pride as men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:44.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that’s a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the five of us will go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss you!{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Soccer field}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone’s there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’ve come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She started dribbling the ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:10.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s the one who wrote the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:16.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have gotten annoyed with us always being so useless that she was driven to doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let’s defend the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:19.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re not losing this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Us men will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t really get it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:26.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, take goalie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way, damn idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic dribble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re full of openings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:39.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! {”be prepared” literally but meh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Noda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ref, that’s a red card right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still going, bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her, TK! Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy come, easy go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:02.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Number three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo! Here we—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:09.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{missing line again}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you’re the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll have to kill me to take this ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of sportsmanship is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Killer Shot!!{必殺殺人 something}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:33.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell whether she wants to kill me or score a goal with this shot! {which I can’t decide if it was intended to kill me or to score a goal!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:35.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It went in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I scored a goal!{ゴールイン出来たんだぜ or somesuch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:51.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To Yui, by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrambled it trouble down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s keep this a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:08.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, she lost the ball, didn’t pass the goalie and went all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s move on to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<Sign: Baseball field >
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:25.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, how far are you trying to hit this home run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the fence, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:35.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well for now, hit it as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hitting the ball doesn’t mean much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the ball carefully and hit it with the center of the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:48.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re hitting too high on the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you’re too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way you’ll hit it with your eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:09.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re too tired to grip properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no point continuing further today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:37.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not going to do it just by yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:42.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s stop here for today, I can’t see the ball anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll start again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:15.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try? Serious baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Full swing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven’t done that in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this kind of thing’s okay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not hitting them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:58.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is why...{I guess it can’t be helped... (like, of course her hands would blister as a noob suddenly doing all this swinging)}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t do it after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough for this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:15.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:18.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because you wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See it through to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:24.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me getting a home run would be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:29.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even without hitting one, I was able to use my body to this extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like going to a club every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:41.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was paralyzed in the past, so this was amazingly fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So they’re all fulfilled?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fulfilled? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:53.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you wanted to do when you couldn’t move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:57.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate happiness for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can’t do housework or cleaning or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I can’t do anything by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m nothing but trouble, dragging everyone else down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess no one would want to take me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,God is pretty mean....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:24.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:37.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:05.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t know the real me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:09.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens to you in the real world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of sickness you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t walk or even stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no matter what kind!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can’t walk or stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you can’t have kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll still marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yui I met here isn’t fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the real Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:44.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where or how I meet you, I’ll fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can meet you again, against the 6 billion to 1 odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:53.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and even if your body can’t move,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:02.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m always in bed at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I play baseball you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:10.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I’ll smash a baseball through your window,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I go to get it, I’ll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s how we’ll meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:25.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll end up talking, we'll get along, and before I know it I’ll be visiting you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:40.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom’s always working hard by herself to take care of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:44.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:49.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:58.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:01.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll help you out till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:05.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still lots of our friends who need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:07.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:54.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did I just cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:57.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:00.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain it a bit more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:02.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the only explanation I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:05.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san just ran here and defeated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:08.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san by himself was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.20,0:24:10.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:12.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is developing an abnormality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He did something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.30,0:24:19.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to drop his glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.11,0:24:20.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a bad dream?{nightmare}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:21.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to save them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.34,0:24:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:23.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too irregular..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s coming, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:24.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even being erased by Angel would be better than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:24.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:24.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:26.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:27.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we can, we’ll meet again.
