Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:53.28,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}I have no regrets over what has been born
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:22:06.17,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}Like the feeling after a festival, it’s sad but we should move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:17.17,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}I’ll go anywhere, you know that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:25.40,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}I’ll grant your dream of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:33.26,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}Even if I’m parted from you, no matter how far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:41.13,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}I’ll be born again with the new morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:49.20,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}The twists and turns of time will change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:57.24,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}I don’t remember what happened anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:05.22,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}But when I close my eyes, someone’s beside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:13.81,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\an8}Somehow right now, that’s my greatest treasure
